# Dockerfile-scoped ignore for the control-plane image (BuildKit picks this over
# the repo-root .dockerignore, which excludes apps/ for the hub build). We keep
# apps/cloud + packages/ but drop the other apps and the site to slim the context.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.log
.git
.github
apps/web
apps/electron
apps/expo
site
docs
